[normal] BIS research paper No 76, May 2012.  The proportion satisfied rose to 92% amongst completers.
[normal] The AELP responses to the APPG Local Growth skills inquiry and the APPG consultation, 
[normal]Rising to the challenge: how LEPs can deliver local growth
[normal] strategies set out our position on localism and LEPs in more detail.
[normal] 
[normal]Going in the right direction? Careers guidance in schools from September 2012
[normal].  Report by Ofsted published in September 2013.
